org.linphone.core.tutorials

Class TutorialRegistration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linphone.core.tutorials.TutorialRegistration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LinphoneCoreListener

    public class TutorialRegistration
extends java.lang.Object
implements LinphoneCoreListener
    This program is a _very_ simple usage example of liblinphone. Demonstrating how to initiate a SIP registration from a sip uri identity passed from the command line. First argument must be like sip:jehan@sip.linphone.org, second must be password.
    ex registration sip:jehan@sip.linphone.org secret Ported from registration.c
